{"tid":751761,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗撚正式收皮","createTime":"2018-07-22T07:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T17:50:26.000Z","uid":82917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb50a4ae63fc31793ec28b9acf21122f4f64a52","tid":751761,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/150636_51df83445b8402a6bb741ff8e9117f5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F150636_51df83445b8402a6bb741ff8e9117f5d.png&h=12e18678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣布敗走寵物台！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n心灰意冷的小美<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/150752_df22d4ea518f7520efdf4b2b171349d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F150752_df22d4ea518f7520efdf4b2b171349d3.png&h=0b22bd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好嬲啊啊啊啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/150815_2e288d4eea9ea862cee69b0bbd1bafb9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F150815_2e288d4eea9ea862cee69b0bbd1bafb9.png&h=bbfeceba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去街街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/150856_ed633c6fc6264279f71238e6e93326b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F150856_ed633c6fc6264279f71238e6e93326b2.png&h=2e64118e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再去街街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/150925_9cd4d558fcc896a224601588fb300124.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F150925_9cd4d558fcc896a224601588fb300124.png&h=29412648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗公<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151545_b410a910c28fdce63c420e6b1617ea52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151545_b410a910c28fdce63c420e6b1617ea52.png&h=7fd7cd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151642_297e2d2750b672ac848cfe56e390001b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151642_297e2d2750b672ac848cfe56e390001b.png&h=7272d0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺狗屎會唔會比人bam？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">慎入！多屎！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151438_ff3306c714e853ced6179c1defc6f00f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151438_ff3306c714e853ced6179c1defc6f00f.png&h=3fd1aedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/151518_6b23681d43b218584e5b0ac19c0d4737.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F151518_6b23681d43b218584e5b0ac19c0d4737.png&h=b6618718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝朝都臭醒左，一起身就作嘔，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲要好撚開心搖哂尾同我宣示主權咁<br />\n「早晨香唔香呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 roommate隻狗，好鍾意你好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bc98cb3cf68f325c3c3ce35a6b551ce3a6e249","tid":751761,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets